In order to create the first ndk android application

follow :
http://tools.android.com/recent/usingthendkplugin

1. Set the path of ndk to the folder that contains the ndk
Preferences -> Android -> NDK -> folder

2. Right click on the android project and select Android tools
Add native support -> Finish

Alternatively, you can create a jni folder using:
https://thenewcircle.com/s/post/49/using_ndk_to_call_c_code_from_android_apps
